@startuml seq_slides_flow
title Slides Flow (Current Code, C2)

actor "Trainer" as Trainer
database "PPTX Sources\n(PPTX_WATCH_DIR or PPTX_CATALOG_FILE)" as PptxSources
participant "Slides Daemon\n(slides_daemon.py)" as Daemon
database "Published PDFs\n(PPTX_PUBLISH_DIR=materials/slides)" as MaterialsSlides
participant "Workshop Backend\n(FastAPI)" as Backend
participant "Participant UI\n(static/participant.js)" as PaxUI
actor "Participant" as Pax

== Daemon Publish Cycle ==

Trainer -> PptxSources : Update .pptx
Daemon -> PptxSources : Poll tracked sources
Daemon -> Daemon : Convert changed .pptx -> PDF
Daemon -> MaterialsSlides : Copy PDF to publish_dir
Daemon -> Backend : POST /api/slides/current\n{url, slug, source_file}
Daemon -> Backend : POST /api/quiz-status\n{status, message, slides:[...]}

note right of Backend
  /api/quiz-status updates state.slides
  /api/slides/current updates state.slides_current
end note

== Participant Slides View ==

Pax -> PaxUI : Open Slides modal
PaxUI -> Backend : GET /api/slides (no-store)
Backend -> MaterialsSlides : Build local index of PDFs
Backend -> Backend : Merge (priority order):\n1) local_materials\n2) state.slides\n+ append slides_current if present
Backend --> PaxUI : {slides:[name,slug,url,updated_at,...]}

alt slides empty
  PaxUI -> Pax : Show "No slides published yet"
else slides available
  PaxUI -> Pax : Populate combo box
  PaxUI -> Backend : GET /api/slides/file/{slug}\n(for local_materials entries)
  Backend -> MaterialsSlides : Resolve slug -> file path
  MaterialsSlides --> Backend : PDF bytes
  Backend --> PaxUI : application/pdf
  PaxUI -> Pax : Render PDF.js preview
end

loop every 30s while modal open
  PaxUI -> Backend : GET /api/slides (no-store)
  Backend --> PaxUI : refreshed merged catalog
end

note over PaxUI, Backend
  Catalog is global for the whole session.
  No filtering by participant UUID.
end note

@enduml
